5d0e9ce7fb867c79f84d4d17b06e03ff:
query QContractQuery(
  $subscriberId: ID!
) {
  contract(subscriberId: $subscriberId) {
    externalId
    effectDate
    numberOfBeneficiaries
    subscriber {
      externalId
      isBeneficiary
      civility
      firstName
      lastName
      fullName
      birthName
      birthDate
      nic
      address
      zipCode
      city
      email
      phone
    }
    beneficiaries {
      externalId
      civility
      beneficiaryType
      firstName
      lastName
      fullName
      nic
      birthDate
    }
    payments {
      iban
      ribUploadId
      ribFilename
    }
  }
}
e692c8f1ca88ec0ecce5a8456c31fd22:
query QBeneficiariesQuery(
  $subscriberId: ID!
) {
  getBeneficiaries(subscriberId: $subscriberId) {
    id
    subscriber {
      externalId
      civility
      isBeneficiary
      firstName
      lastName
      fullName
      birthName
      birthDate
      nic
      address
      zipCode
      city
      email
      phone
    }
    beneficiaries {
      externalId
      civility
      beneficiaryType
      firstName
      lastName
      fullName
      nic
    }
    numberOfBeneficiaries
  }
}
